      "zh": "卷六 補帝紀第六 孝昭帝",
      "en": "Volume 6 Annals 6: Emperor Xiaozhao",
      "raw": "卷六 補帝紀第六 孝昭帝 Volume 6 Annals 6: Emperor Xiaozhao"
    },
    "sentenceCount": 153,
    "translatedCount": 0,
    "glossarySize": 39676,
    "scrapedAt": "2026-04-25T21:53:07.302Z",
